CA CMS Collaboration
TI Search for leptophobic Z ' bosons decaying into four-lepton final states
   in proton-proton collisions at root s=8 TeV

CA CMS Collaboration
TI Search for direct production of super symmetric partners of the top
   quark in the all-jets final state in proton-proton collisions at root
   s=13 TeV
